A multi-objective improved AO (MOIAO) was developed by Long et al. [81] to solve optimal reactive power dispatch. This approach incorporates a probabilistic perturbation method to improve the equilibrium between global exploitation and local exploration. The MOIAO is utilized to achieve optimal performance in terms of the Ploss\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
